.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Parameters
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBv\fP (\fI\%fy_generic\fP) – An out\-of\-place non\-collection generic value.
.IP \(bu 2
\fBd\fP (ptrdiff_t) – Byte delta to add to the embedded pointer.
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
