.B fy_generic_get_default(_colv, _key, _dv) 
Get an element from a collection by key or index, typed via default.
.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Parameters
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fB_colv\fP – Collection value (fy_generic, sequence handle, or mapping handle)
.IP \(bu 2
