fy_generic and used as the lookup key. For sequences, \fB_key\fP is coerced to a size_t index.
Accepts fy_generic, fy_generic_sequence_handle, or fy_generic_mapping_handle as \fB_colv\fP\&.
.SS Return
.sp
The element at \fB_key\fP cast to the type of \fB_dv\fP, or \fB_dv\fP if not found or wrong type.
